reviewText: Bree Olson is amazing she really likes it

The dvd was of interest to me ,but I was unable to watch it as It would not play on either of my two dvd players, the seller suggested it may be because they are not new enough machines. Because of the additional shipping fees I would pay to return it and the 50% restocking fees it would cost if me if the seller says it is not defective. It is simply not worth losing more money over for a relatively small sale to begin with. I am less than happy so ( lesson learned ) I guess I will give it away to someone with a new dvd player or just put it in the garbage. Thanks
A really awesome movie. This girl is talented and awesome.
